Title: XAML Cleaner AddIn
Description:
XamlCleaner is a small add-in utility what makes it easier for developers and designers to clean xaml filles of unused and duplicates namespace references. In addition include a WPF application project to pharser xaml files out freely Visual Studio.

It's developed in C#
